from the end of the data area; on a 32-bit platform, the indexes of the
bytes are:

@example
   1st word    2nd word    3rd word    4th word
|-----------|-----------|-----------|-----------|
                        |--|--|--|--|--|--|--|--| bytes
                          7  6  5  4  3  2  1  0  offsets
